dct_title_s: Tegucigalpa, Honduras, C.A.: hoja no. 3, sector S.E
dct_description_sm: Honduras. Instituto Geografico Nacional. North Decimal Degree 14.083300. South Decimal Degree 14.0333. East Decimal Degree -87.1333. West Decimal Degree -87.2000. Alternate title: Tegucigalpa, hoja no. 3, sector S.E. In upper left margin: Tegucigalpa escala 1:10,000. Universal transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 4 m. contour interval and spot heights. With an index to locate governamental buildings, hospitals, military establishments, and public service installations.
